              "free_text": [
                " 54 He-3 neutron detectors placed around",
                "an assembly of Si detectors consisting of a 48x48-strip",
                "focal-plane detector and 4 tunnel 16-strip detectors",
                "for fission fragments and alpha-particle registration.",
                "The neutron detector efficiency measured with a 248Cm",
                "source was (45 +- 1)%.",
                "Average neutron life-time in the assembly is",
                " (23+-1) microsec ."
